{"tid":940071,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"[求救] 電腦成日死機畫面&聲卡住，重開機冇訊號","createTime":"2018-12-13T15:40:10.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-15T14:19:07.000Z","uid":46223,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"fcca60f7b0f132b5d51e4a6eed6c3a5ffc854a35","tid":940071,"uid":46223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-13T15:40:10.000Z","msg":"求救各位巴打 身為毒撚 連部腦都拋棄我<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n打機/睇片成日會死機 死機果時成個畫面停左 有時啲聲會繼續聽到 有時連聲都卡埋<br />\nboot完機 開機果刻2-3秒風扇轉得好快 之後變到好靜 <br />\n機箱燈有著而個mon會顯示冇訊號 呢個狀況hold好耐都冇反應<br />\n每次熄電源後5-10分鐘先成功重開load到windows<br />\n最近成日死機 想知係咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n救救小弟<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"18d815d29fec6f36d10f536ab5cea5dd4f2d1757","tid":940071,"uid":95172,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-13T15:52:05.000Z","msg":"可能係中毒 / hdd / display card。。。<br />\n<br />\n1. 睇下部機用了幾耐，hdd有冇bad sector果d<br />\n<br />\n2. 唔睇唔緊要， 搞病毒, backup data, reset window<br />\n<br />\n3. 換過部機去<br />\n<br />\n是但你啦，冇電腦咪睇手機，手機都可以駁mon睇片/打下機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"658662de1abe06bbda14e509b033f2fe645d98ae","tid":940071,"uid":218086,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-13T15:53:05.000Z","msg":"call硬件傳心師<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4bb1ad232ef75937f29f49d54cc4ff729280cc79","tid":940071,"uid":95172,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-13T15:53:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>可能係中毒 / hdd / display card。。。<br />\n<br />\n1. 睇下部機用了幾耐，hdd有冇bad sector果d<br />\n<br />\n2. 唔睇唔緊要， <span style=\"color: red;\"><del>搞</del></span>病毒, backup data, reset window<br />\n<br />\n3. 換過部機去<br />\n<br />\n是但你啦，冇電腦咪睇手機，手機都可以駁mon睇片/打下機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n掃， 又打錯字<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93aff038db8fdb49fcbc1fa260f7efad10d1b3ee","tid":940071,"uid":85659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-13T15:56:28.000Z","msg":"似DISPLAY"},{"pid":"00edee0e52bc4b8927cbb2216bc97fa98e0d38c8","tid":940071,"uid":55870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"93aff038db8fdb49fcbc1fa260f7efad10d1b3ee","tid":940071,"uid":85659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-13T15:56:28.000Z","msg":"似DISPLAY"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-14T00:56:35.000Z","msg":"我都認為係display問題<br />\n你部機咩spec幾多年機呀？"},{"pid":"bb02bb60a9091910e8a6699f4fa6f6a33e639dc7","tid":940071,"uid":85659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-14T10:26:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c60859ade89bda7432e012599bbf64b50ea5575","tid":940071,"uid":220085,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-14T10:31:49.000Z","msg":"我都係差唔多情況<br />\n新機<br />\n試過換display card唔得<br />\n2條ram拆走一條就無問題<br />\n通常都係打下game就卡死畫面<br />\n但係2條ram分開都無問題<br />\n2條ram一模一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4361795d9f344908d6ec55b539c1f30aeb7f6822","tid":940071,"uid":128053,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-14T10:34:25.000Z","msg":"可能係火牛老化<br />\n我都試過 拎埋display卡去保養<br />\n佢話有可能火牛老化唔夠力<br />\n叫我拎走一隻harddisk 試<br />\n最後真係冇事"},{"pid":"bd7e9acf22d7cab0120012ae8836304ea3a8b321","tid":940071,"uid":36157,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-14T11:56:55.000Z","msg":"死火牛"},{"pid":"30a6a5631fd7d34c8b91eebb01b275fc629ea3ae","tid":940071,"uid":55870,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-14T13:07:08.000Z","msg":"邊有咁多火牛唔夠用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59daea6446ea58ed8d07dd5e5ec1c46d2573e169","tid":940071,"uid":55870,